<view class="page-contact page-safe-bottom">
  <view class="hint">{{hint}}</view>
  <view class="poster-wrap">
    <image
      class="poster"
      src="{{posterUrl}}"
      mode="widthFix"
      show-menu-by-longpress="{{true}}"
      lazy-load="{{false}}"
      binderror="onPosterError"
    />
  </view>
  <view class="tip" wx:if="{{isNetworkPoster}}">长按图片，选择「识别图中二维码」</view>
  <view class="tip tip-warn" wx:else>
    当前为本地预览图，微信不支持识别包内图片中的二维码。请到管理后台「联系店长」上传海报后，真机即可长按识别；也可先保存到相册再扫一扫。
  </view>
  <view class="save-btn" bindtap="savePoster">保存图片到相册</view>
</view>
